  "title": "Resident Technical Officers (HDB BTO)",
  "description": "<p>1. to carry out the supervision of building works as stipulated in the Building Control Act</p>\n<p>2. to co-ordinate and supervise the defects investigation and rectification Works</p>\n<p>3. verify that the Contractor’s defects rectification are completed satisfactorily, or to the satisfaction of HDB;</p>\n<p>4. monitor and track that the defects rectification meet the service standards set;</p>\n<p>5. Keep proper site documentation and records</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>BCA-registered / NCCS / BCSS</li>\n  <li>Min 3 yrs experience in the supervision of C&amp;S/Architectural works preferably in HDB BTO projects</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please send your resume to posts@jgp-group.com and indicate the position you are applying clearly. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Only shortlisted applicants will be notified. </p>",
